name: The Windows - Storming on the Block
description:
Celebrating life, celebrating one of my biggest ifluences (The Doors) and NFT's with you guys!
Since this journey started, i never felt powerless or invisible again.
This is why i don't mind GIVING AWAY this awesome song, I have a lot more where this one came from. We are infinite.
